Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.91,0:01:04.83,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\bord0\c&H8B5546&\pos(620,425)}Misunderstood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:20.96,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,About what I said that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:22.52,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:24.74,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.02,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:35.55,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That what he said before wasn't important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.71,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he must've meant that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that much should have been obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.63,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It should have been obvious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:54.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I considered myself the closest to you out of all of the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.05,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.84,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:04.65,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,and how I should've answered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:10.83,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:11.98,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.37,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be this upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.70,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no sense for me to be this upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.16,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:27.31,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who thought it meant something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.40,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.88,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:34.84,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.98,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What did we have to come all the way out here to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.23,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:47.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally in the same class as the popular \NKazehaya. It's only normal to want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:49.85,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.99,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on. Just sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:09.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So how many times have you been \Nconfessed to? Do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.04,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.60,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.50,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:22.18,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's been sort of an outcast since freshmen year, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.14,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be better to leave her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.25,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you can't stop helping people like her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.45,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you think you're actually doing more harm than good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.35,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:42.02,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You call Kuronuma an outcast and then \Nsay that I can't leave outcasts alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.16,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.47,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I hit a nerve?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.24,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:57.63,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see a Mr. Lively Smile! Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(200,608)\frz24.179}Irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:02.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I don't want to hear it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:08.18,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.94,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't involve yourself with her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.20,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally being accepted in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:21.34,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But if the girls start getting jealous of her \Nbecause you pay so much attention to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.95,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,she'll become an outcast again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.82,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,That would defeat your purpose too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.66,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:40.39,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.34,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that happened, I would take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason why I do the things I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.81,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.25,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.86,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,the more you do, the more she'll stand out as a target of jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.81,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,She has all these false expectations. I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:09.33,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying that. Why do you feel sorry for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:20.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,When has she ever had false expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:28.76,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:33.47,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You and Sadako have wildly different expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:39.03,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not close enough to her to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.00,Default,Kezehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mea—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.57,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.40,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I'd be giving away a girl's deepest secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.04,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to make things difficult for her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.87,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.37,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.31,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.17,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks in advance then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:08.01,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're so popular, yet you don't have a \Ngirlfriend. Does that mean you like someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.39,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:13.73,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You should go out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.89,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help you get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.11,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:30.15,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not close enough to her to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.99,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What don't I understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.50,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not close enough to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.30,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.28,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.73,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.89,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.57,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.60,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Really, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.34,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like a relatives-only ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:15.77,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're not even inviting their coworkers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.59,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,so I assumed that I wouldn't be invited either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.25,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:27.99,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But then Toru called me and told me that I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.33,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You're like one of the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.58,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Were you happy he called?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:42.73,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm going to go, I have to look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.27,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.21,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll look great in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.03,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.41,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.79,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.28,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Look what I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.13,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I went shopping and couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:15.73,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yano has great taste. I wish I could've shown Sawako too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.59,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sawako go home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.56,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.32,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:35.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think Kuronuma and I are really that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:41.28,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really not understand her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.17,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't really think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:52.70,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even know that Sawako likes him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.51,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Just something someone said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.50,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoelace is untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:10.31,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:17.03,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I actually thought I understood her better than just about everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.04,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Like, people have had the wrong idea about Yano-chin and I before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:25.21,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We've dealt with our share of gossip and lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:30.04,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe not as much as Sawako has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:34.45,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,And Ryu too. He's always been fourth to \Nbat... always the clean up guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:38.40,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,The upperclassmen on the team are really tough on him sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:39.97,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:46.28,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,In that respect, in terms of experience, \Nyou're probably the most different from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.11,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.59,Italics,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.42,Italics,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with him and Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.60,Italics,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.86,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Sawako ran a review session?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:19.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, supposedly she was really good at explaining things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.17,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Kazehaya to plan something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That loud, flamboyant guy did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Kent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:36.11,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kent supposedly volunteered her \Nfor it right in the middle of class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.65,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Miura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.58,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't over think, don't over think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:58.01,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.55,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.16,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.29,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.30,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.84,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.36,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.83,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I kind of felt like he was avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.80,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.72,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy90\bord2\c&H1E2A26&\frz353.784\move(597,429,597,512,0,2863)\3c&H455554&}Entry Prohibited
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.21,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:05.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What did you and Kazehaya talk about \Nyesterday that made things today so awkward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:08.45,Italics,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone else saw this, they'd \Ndefinitely think Sawako's being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.67,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, you spoke with him twice, and the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:21.80,Signs 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1\pos(901,73)}First Time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:21.48,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I considered myself the closest to you out of all of the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:25.18,Signs 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\be1\pos(901,73)}Second Time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:25.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about what I said that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.86,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And the second was like that. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:29.99,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.10,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting impatient...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:39.02,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And you! Why did you give \N chocolates to everyone but him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.83,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That was such a good chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.35,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You two even went to the shrine together on New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:50.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just said it was in thanks, like you always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:53.90,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,He gave you his contact info, didn't he? Didn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.49,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yano-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:13:02.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that hard to meet up with him! Or to give \Nhim chocolates! Any excuse to do it would've worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:09.07,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:16.74,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:23.15,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that. I just don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:28.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bring myself to give him chocolates just in thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.60,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to contact him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:39.17,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous when I'm around him that I can't even greet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.76,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.61,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:52.72,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop myself from being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.44,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't the only one who's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:03.32,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, would you really like things to stay the way they are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:10.96,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,If you decide not to do anything just because \Nyou're scared, things will stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:15.08,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want that, then you need to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.01,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.12,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:25.91,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that you can do in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.26,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,So just calm down and think about it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.26,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:43.03,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever's on duty today for year 2 class \ND, report to the office immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:45.49,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:51.45,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what we were going to do when Sawako started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:55.33,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But you knew exactly what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.50,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,... Nakamura from the class next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.25,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt! What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.21,Alt,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:10.93,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Drop your act. Stop avoiding Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.70,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.56,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.23,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not avoiding her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.64,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Then make it seem like you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:26.71,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,She's used to people avoiding her so \Nstop giving her reason to suspect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.63,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:44.71,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Everyone just keeps saying whatever they please! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.63,Italics,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.78,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You seem to be in a pretty bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.45,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad. I lost my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Lost your temper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:07.53,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt kind of bad for Kazehaya too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.69,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you feel bad for Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:21.70,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause... I mean, the girl he likes \Nacts like she's super scared of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.50,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kazehaya likes someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.28,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sawako? This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:35.92,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But Yano-chin, Kazehaya cares about Sawako too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Like yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.65,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday he—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.31,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.31,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya likes—!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.48,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.61,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.55,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.82,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't one! That's what I've been saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.58,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.83,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.16,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.29,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:10.21,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Kazehaya's the type who \Nlikes people interfering in his business?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.71,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,In middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:19.59,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kazehaya, Eri says she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.80,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:22.43,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.10,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you the one telling me and not her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:25.77,Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,266)\clip(648,238,801,251)}Totally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:25.81,Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,266)\clip(653,240,807,280)}Totally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.10,Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,266)}Totally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.06,Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,446)\clip(645,420,816,459)}Serious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.10,Signs 3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,446)}Serious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.44,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:36.53,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. If we tell Kazehaya and he thinks she \Nasked us to do it, it'll make things worse for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.74,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We can tell Sawako and get her to confess to Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:51.36,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,If we tell Sawako and force her to \Nconfess, they might start going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.36,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,But would that really be for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.31,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,If Sawako's still afraid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:04.79,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be a couple in name only. \NTheir actual situation wouldn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.37,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:13.61,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Sawako to date him while still feeling inferior to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:21.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to come up with the strength to confess to him on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:30.82,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,They both like each other. It'd be wrong for her to \Nfeel like he's just dating her out of pity or kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.08,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:44.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, even if we did tell \NSawako, she probably wouldn't believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.83,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:57.24,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.87,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't really think you understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.12,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably the most different from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.75,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}Different... Different... Different... Different...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.38,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.44,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right. You were saying something about Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.59,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kazehaya? No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:26.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! If I don't fix this, Yano-chin'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? You went to the cursed review session?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the rumors said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Losing five kilograms in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:43.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.87,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:50.08,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be healthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.04,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.92,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,They're complimenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sada—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Will you hold one today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,See? You've got to be more confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:31.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.96,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, don't thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:40.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that plant from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That's a medicinal herb I'm growing in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Medicinal herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.24,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:52.75,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:21:00.65,Italics,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,... the more you do, the more she'll \Nstand out as a target of jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.14,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What... should I do?
